          "TITLE": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": null,
              "free_text": [
                "Charge Distribution for Light Mass Fission Products",
                " in the Thermal Neutron Induced Fission of 229Th,",
                " 241Pu, 245Cm and 252Cf(SF)."
              ]
            }
          ],
          "AUTHOR": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": [
                "H.Naik",
                "S.P.Dange",
                "R.J.Singh"
              ],
              "free_text": [
                ""
              ]
            }
          ],
          "INSTITUTE": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": [
                "3INDTRM"
              ],
              "free_text": [
                ""
              ]
            }
          ],
          "REFERENCE": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": {
                "code": "J,RCA,83,109,1998",
                "code_unit": [
                  {
                    "unit": "J,RCA,83,109,1998",
                    "doi": "10.1524/ract.1998.83.3.109",
                    "field": {
                      "reference_type": "J",
                      "reference": {
                        "code": "RCA",
                        "number": null,
                        "volume": "83",
                        "part": null,
                        "issue": null,
                        "page": "109"
                      },
                      "date": 1998
                    }
                  }
                ],
                "unit_combination": "(%)"
              },
              "free_text": [
                ""
              ]
            }
          ],
          "FACILITY": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": {
                "facility": [
                  "REAC"
                ],
                "institute": "3INDTRM"
              },
              "free_text": [
                " Research reactor CIRUS using pneumatic",
                " facility for irradiation for short lived products.",
                "Research (Swimming Pool Type) reactor APSARA for long",
                " lived fission products."
              ]
            }
          ],
          "SAMPLE": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": null,
              "free_text": [
                "For shortlived fission products nitrate solution of",
                " 229Th (10 ug), 241Pu (2 ug), 245Cm (1 ug) sealed in",
                " polypropelebne tubes were irradiated for 5 seconds to",
                " 30 minutes using pneumatic carrier facility of CIRUS",
                " reactor at a flux  of 5x10**12 n/cm2/sec.",
                "For long lived fission products, electrodeposited",
                " target of 229Th (100 ug), 241Pu (25 ug), and 245Cm",
                " (4 ug) were irradiated in the APSARA   reactor for",
                " 5-60 minutes at a flux of 1.2x10**12 n/cm2/sec.",
                "In case of 252Cf(SF) recoil fission products were",
                " collected on Al foil from an electrodeposited source",
                " -(3 ug)"
              ]
            }
          ],
          "DETECTOR": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": [
                "HPGE"
              ],
              "free_text": [
                " 80 c.c. HPGe detector connected to a PC based",
                " 4K channel analyzer.",
                "Resolution of the detector system was 2.0 keV at 1332",
                " keV of 60Co."
              ]
            }
          ],
          "METHOD": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": [
                "REC",
                "GSPEC"
              ],
              "free_text": [
                " Collection of fission products using",
                " recoil catcher technique, off line gamma ray",
                " spectrometric analysis of fission products in the",
                " irradiated sample."
              ]
            }
          ],
          "ANALYSIS": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": null,
              "free_text": [
                "Photo-peak areas were obtained from the gamma rays of",
                " light fission products;",
                " a) 229Th(n,f): 86Br, 90Kr, 91,92,93,94Sr 95Y, 97Zr",
                " b) 241Pu(n,f): 91,92,94Sr, 97Zr, 105Tc",
                " c) 245Cm(n,f): 90Kr,91,92,94Sr,97Zr, 108,109Ru, 112Pd",
                " d) 252Cf(sf): 106Tc"
              ]
            },
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": [
                "DECAY"
              ],
              "free_text": [
                " Their cumulative yields - (CY) were determined",
                " using decay equation.",
                "From the cumulative yields, FCY were determined using",
                " mass chain yield from literature.",
                "FCY of some fission products like 91,92Sr,97Zr were",
                " determined using decay growth equation.",
                "From the FCY values, the most probable charge, width",
                " parameter sigma-Z and charge polarization delta-Z",
                " were deduced."
              ]
            }
          ],
          "ERR-ANALYS": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": {
                "heading": "DATA-ERR",
                "minimum_value": null,
                "maximum_value": null,
                "correlation_property": null
              },
              "free_text": [
                " The error in th FCY of the light mass",
                " fission products is precissional error due to",
                " replicate measurement."
              ]
            }
          ],
